    <item>
      <title>日本将利用更多税收激励措施鼓励工资上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/japan-to-use-more-tax-incentives-to-encourage-wage-increases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本自民党及其联盟伙伴公明党同意向大幅提高工资的公司提供更多税收优惠，这可能有助于提高日本实现央行削减刺激措施所需的工资增长和通胀良性循环的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/japan-to-use-more-tax-incentives-to-encourage-wage-increases</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 06:12:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
