    <item>
      <title>印度石油需求增长将在经历丰收后于 2024 年逐渐减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/oil-demand-growth-in-india-to-taper-in-2024-after-bumper-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着疫情后消费激增的消退，印度这个主要亚洲市场的石油需求增长预计明年将放缓，这与中国经济放缓相呼应，并对价格带来新的阻力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/oil-demand-growth-in-india-to-taper-in-2024-after-bumper-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 03:11:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员关注美联储转向，美元跌至八月以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/dollar-drops-to-weakest-since-august-as-fed-weighs-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美元周四跌至四个月低点，因为交易员消化了迄今为止最明确的信号，即美联储激进的加息行动已经结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/dollar-drops-to-weakest-since-august-as-fed-weighs-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 01:07:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
